Hey Claude, I'd like to automate the release process into one `justfile` command taking a new version number as arg, doing the following steps:\

- Update `CHANGELOG.md` based on the commit messages since the last tag\
- Commit the changes in these 3 files\
- Push the commit\
- Tag the commit with `Release x.x.x`\
- Push the tag to `origin`
